++ Trigger Anything

DLA means that there should be [Triggers] for every event or state.

++Implementation

The ability to trigger everything is an important AvailableOption that allows [Users] to ImplementTheUnimplemented themselves. AutoInterface could be used to help create interfaces for the triggers they setup.

++Examples

System clock
    * every second/minute/hour/day
    * in x
    * at x

